Packages:
    npm i chalk@4.1.2
    npm install yargs --save
    npm install nodemon   //node monitor
    npm install lodash --save


Todo list using node js
    input using command line arguments.
    To add into the list: node app.js addTodo --title="Project" --list="project1,project2"
    To list todo: node app.js listTodos
    To delete todo: node app.js deleteTodo --title="Project"
    To search/display todo: node app.js readTodo --title="Project" 
    
